<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Turpitude" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Turpitude,</orth> extreme baseness and depravity: <cit><quote>minds swayed by eyes are full of t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.2.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 2, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my t. thou dost so crown with gold,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.6.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 6, 33</bibl></cit>.
